Data Scraping
------------------
- More than one information collection process is Data Scraping
- Mainly use for many product information collection at a time
- class video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pulWJJYqdLM

Data Scraping Extension Install
--------------------------
- Open chrome browser and type "Instant data scraper" and press enter
- click on "Instant Data Scraper" from chromewebstore.google.com
- click on "Add to Chrome" button
- now, click on Extention icon (beside the address bar of chrome browser) --> Intant Data Scraper (click on pin icon)

How to Collect Data and Tranfer to excel file
-----------------------------------------------
Collect Data:
- Open chrome browser and search product (E-Commerce site)
- click on "Instant Data Scraper" icon (at the side of chrome browser address bar) --> ON/English (click)
- click on "Locate Next Button" of Instant Data Scraper and scroll down chrome browser (product page) to pagination area and click on pagination "Next" button
- click on "Sart crawling" button of Instant Data Scraper to start data collection
- when need to stop collection, click on "Stop crawling" button of Instant Data Scraper

Transfer to Excel file:
- to transfer data to Excel file, click on "XLSX" button   // for excel data 
- to transfer data to Google Sheet, click on "COPY ALL" button and open Google Sheet --> create a page by click on "+" --> click on a cell and right click --> paste

How to Set Serial Number (1-100) auto in excel sheet
---------------------------------
- click a cell and type 1
- Fill --> Series 
	- Series is "Columns"
	- Type "Linear"
	- Step value: 1       Stop value:100        // 1-100

